<h2><%= @event.location %></h2>
<h3><%= @event.start %></h3>
<%= "<em>You are currently RSVP'd as #{current_user.rsvp_for(@event)} for this event!</em><br /><br />".html_safe if current_user.rsvp_for(@event) %>
Update your RSVP: <%= link_to("Yes", rsvp_path(@event, "yes"), method: :patch) %>, <%= link_to("No", rsvp_path(@event, "no"), method: :patch) %>, <%= link_to("Maybe", rsvp_path(@event, "maybe"), method: :patch) %>